<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> rājarāja</hi> tevarkku yāṇṭu <num value="17"><g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num><g type="dash"/>vatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattu tiruveṅkaṭakkoṭṭattup perumpāṇappāṭi Āṟṟūrnāṭṭut
<lb n="2"/>tirukkāḷattiyāṉa mummuṭicoḻapurattu nāyaṉār tirukkāḷattiuṭaiya nāyaṉārkku tiyākacamuttirappaṭṭaiyār poṉṉi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>aracar makaṉ vimaracaṉ tiruṉuntāviḷakku Oṉṟukku viṭṭa pacu muppattiraṇṭum I<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>pam Oṉṟum Ikkoyil tiruviḷakku
<lb n="4" break="no"/>iṭaiyaril Ai<unclear>y</unclear>ñcūrnāṭṭil(p) paruttiyūril Irukkum māvaṭuttakkoṉ <unclear>viḷa</unclear>kkuk k<unclear>ālu</unclear>m ciṉṉakkoṉ viḷakkuk kālum toṇṭ<unclear>ai</unclear>māṉāṟṟūril
<lb n="5"/>Irukkum peṟṟikkoṉ viḷakkaraiyum Āka viḷakkoṉṟukkum nāḷ Oṉṟukkut tirukkāḷattiuṭaiyāṉāl Aḷakkum ney Uḻakkum nāṅkaḷum Eṅkaḷ va
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟkkattāri luḷḷārum cantirātittavarai Aḷakkakaṭavomāka camma<supplied reason="omitted">ti</supplied>ttu Upaiyaṅ kaikkoṇṭom <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉmāke<hi rend="grantha">śvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

